You'll need a viewer that doesn't wordwrap to view the wider tables.

Notes:
Conversion wasn't too bad (11-MT = HG in most cases) MT gives all
weapons a 0 modifier at short range, so missiles are 0 short range,
+1 long range, but the combat table makes up for this.

Tractors don't cause damage rolls, instead they lower the agility of
the target ship. (Rules to follow)
Tractors may be used in defense as if they were a repulsor with the same usp 
code.

Targets agility is used as a negative DM to all starship combat in MT,
but only to Meson Guns and PA's in HG (it's listed as a modifier on
P47 but not p45). Assuming HG is correct which new weapons should be
affected by targets agility?

J.

